captions.text: Ro: Hey guys, it’s Ro!

Ro: And I’m here with my sister Mo today.
Mo: Hello!

Ro: Yeah, and our last video that we did together
we asked you guys:

Ro: What kind of fun game you would like to
see next? And, we got

Ro: so many requests for… Mo: Chubby Bunny!
Ro: Chubby Bunny!

Ro: So let’s talk about advantages vs disadvantages,
our personal

Ro: advantage vs disadvantages. I’ll go
first are you ready? Mo: Yeah.

Ro: Disadvantage, I have a small mouth. We
are petite in general and

Ro: my mouth is just extra petite. I had a
retainer called an expander,

Ro: and that is, every 2 weeks, for those
of you who don’t know, the

Ro: orthodontist would twist it and it would
expand just a little bit and

Ro: it would actually expand my jaw. It was
very painful, but it was because

Ro: our mouths were too small. Mo: Yeah I
had, I had the same thing and

Mo: we had to wear sweet little packs around
our necks to put it in when we ate.
Ro: Super, we were the cool kids!
Mo: That was great. Ro: A lot of… This goin on!

Mo: Well I think an advantage that I have
is that I used to suck on my fist

Mo: when I was little, instead of my thumb.
Ro: Hahaha, it’s true!

Mo: And so, I think I can fit a lot of marshmallows
in there.

Ro: We had to put a sock over her hand so
she would stop sucking on her fist.

Ro: My advantage, over Mo… I love marshmallows!
Mo: Haha yeah!

Ro: So, what are the rules because, I’ve
never played. So how do you do this?

Mo: OK, well you, this is how I play Chubby
Bunny. Um, one person will

Mo: go first and put the marshmallow in their
mouth and they have to say

Mo: Chubby Bunny. Ro: Chubby Bunny. Mo: And
then the next person will and

Mo: they’ll have to put in another marshmallow
and say Chubby Bunny. And,

Mo: the person who can’t fit another marshmallow
in or can’t say Chubby Bunny loses

Both: Rock, Paper, Scissors. Rock, Paper,
Scissors. Rock, Paper, Scissors.

Ro: Ohh! Mo: Wait, do I start or do you start?
Ro: Yeah! Oh wait, is it
Ro: an advantage to start?
Mo: I don’t know…
Ro: Mo! You’re supposed to tell me the rules!
Mo: Here we go, first one!

Ro: Hahahaha, you’re
like a hamster!
Mo: Chubby Bunny! Your turn.

Ro: OK, this doesn’t look too hard, oh my! That’s
quite large! Oh! Chubby Bunny!
Mo: Yeah! 1 down. Chubby Bunny.

Ro: My 2nd one, oh my! Oh it’s like it’s
full in there. Chubby Bunny!
Mo: OK. Ro: Herwamany yerdasget? Oh my goodness!
Mo: Chubby Bunny!

Ro: 3 this my 3rd, here we go. Where do you
put it?

Mo: Don’t laugh, otherwise it'll… That’s a
disadvantage, is laughing.

Ro: Laughing is a disadvantage? Mo: Yeah cause
your cheeks will push it out.
Ro: Oh I’m screwed! OK, bahahahaha! Ha-ha-heeeeee!
Ro: Chubby Berney.
Mo: Chubby Bunny.
Ro: Cherby bobby. Mo: I heard it!
Mo: Chubby Bunny!
Ro: I can’t! I can’t!
Mo: Chubby Bunny!
Ro: WHOA! No way, whoa!
Mo: Chubby Bunny. Ro: Here, let me help! Hahaha

Mo: Chubby Bunny? Ro: I heard it! I’ll be
ready in case, OK, you keep going girl!
Ro: OK, OK, oh! Pff-ha-ha-ha

Ro: Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo-doo-doo! We have
your official victor, Molly Lu.

Ro: She has won the official bunny ears for
Chubby Bunny! There you go,
Ro: dee-dee-dee-dee-dee! Mo: Heyyy!

Ro: Thanks you guys for suggesting this game,
it was so much fun

Ro: and if you’d like to see our previous
games, you can click here.

Mo: Or up here. And if you’ve played Chubby
Bunny before, leave us a

Mo: comment down below and let us know how
many marshmallows you’ve been

Mo: able to fit into your mouth. Ro: Molly
got 7. Mo: I got 7!

Mo: Rosanna got 4, how many did you get? Ro:
Probably more than 4!

Ro: Dat’s OK doe! I will also be putting,
uh, all of Mo’s links down below

Ro: She has Twitter AND Instagram! Mo: That,
that’s right! Ro: I’m very

Ro: proud of her, she’s new to the inter-webs,
so go check her out, she

Ro: posts lots of cute pictures and she have
her little dog Henry.
Ro: Thanks again you guys, bye-bye! Mo: Bye!

Mo: Ewwah! Oh, my god I blocked that! Ro:
Fire, fire, fire off all cannons!

Mo: I did not know you were doing that! Ro:
Aha! Fire, fire in the hole!

Ro: Fire in the hole! Mo: Ew! This is so gross!
Ro: Fire in the hole!
Ro: Fire in the hole! He-he-he-he Molly!
